	tristate "Winbond W83627HF, W83627THF, W83637HF, W83687THF, W83697HF"
	select HWMON_VID
	help
	  If you say yes here you get support for the Winbond W836X7 series
	  of sensor chips: the W83627HF, W83627THF, W83637HF, W83687THF and
	  W83697HF.

